zadmoni设计架构：
(各文件相见 github)
zadmoni
|-- config
    |-- client
    `-- service
        |-- conf
        |   |-- __init__.py
        |   |-- host.py
        |   |-- host.txt
        |   |-- service
        |   |   |-- __init__.py
        |   |   |-- __init__.pyc
        |   |   |-- generic.py
        |   |   |-- generic.pyc
        |   |   |-- generic.txt
        |   |   |-- linux.py
        |   |   |-- linux.pyc
        |   |   `-- linux.txt
        |   |-- setting.py
        |   |-- setting.pyc
        |   |-- template.py
        |   |-- template.pyc
        |   `-- template.txt
        `-- core
            |-- RedisHelper.txt
            |-- __init__.py
            |-- __init__.pyc
            |-- main.py
            |-- main.pyc
            |-- main.txt
            |-- redishelper.py
            |-- redishelper.pyc
            |-- settings.py
            |-- settings.pyc
